name: A Light At Night
description:
Copperplate etching with aquatint,
 signed and numbered edition of 5

Paper size is approximate due to hand tearing of paper, printed area size 20 x 15 cms, or 8 x 6 inches


Print will ship in postage tube and multiple prints can ship together.

name: Looking Up
description:
Copperplate etching on Fabriano paper,  Looking Up shows the view of the winter bare Silver Birch trees in a park in Minneapolis. 

Edition of 5, signed and numbered. 

Paper size is approx. 25 x 33cm or 10 x 13 inches - 
Actual printed image size is 10 x 15cm, or 4 x 6 inches. 

Please note, that due to each print being hand torn to size, paper size is approximate only and may vary by 1 or 2 cms.

name: Solitude
description:
3 colour reduction lino print. 

Paper is 19 x 15.5 inches, actual printed area is 12 x 12. 

Edition of 5, signed and numbered.

Print will be shipped in an Australia Post tube, multiple prints can ship together for the same price. Shipping calculated at checkout.

name: New Wave 1
description:
New Wave 1 is a Giclee print of an original painting, which was then digitally altered. 

Limited edition (5) signed and numbered, 8.5 x 11.5 inches on Canson Rag 310 gsm archival grade paper, printed with archival grade inks to last a lifetime. 

Print will be shipped in an Australia Post tube, multiple prints can be shipped together for the one shipping price.  Shipping calculated at checkout.

name: Twisted Nursery Rhyme
description:
My Twisted Nursery Rhyme is a little twist on the old Owl and The Pussycat tale...

Giclee print on archival quality Canson Rag 310gsm paper, with archival inks. 

Print measures 17 x 12.5 inches, with a 3/4 inch white border. (A3 size)

Limited edition of 5, signed and numbered. 

Print will be shipped in an Australia Post tube, multiple prints can be shipped together for the one shipping price. Shipping calculated at checkout.
